title: 12/24 Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 16 Recap - Who's #1?
description:
Let's start the show with a look ahead to 2018, who's the #1 pick in Fantasy drafts (4:22)? ... All the latest news you need to know if you're playing in Week 17 (12:00), plus a Week 16 stud (18:05) and dud (21:20) and a look at the playoff picture (23:30) ... Jamey reviews each position with what he got right and wrong at QB (27:12), RB (29:28), WR (30:20) and TE (32:55). Then we look at the Week 16 leaders at each position (33:51) before reviewing each game (49:12) with Fantasy analysis ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
